{
  "id": "6a03e6d30a4dd8dcd26f4831",
  "title": "メタ構文変数のように「罵詈雑言」という悪態をつきたい",
  "created": 1778640597,
  "updated": 1778640601,
  "lines": [
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d30a4dd8dcd26f4831",
      "text": "メタ構文変数のように「罵詈雑言」という悪態をつきたい",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420e8",
      "text": "from [2026/04/08]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420e9",
      "text": "",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640601
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420ea",
      "text": "[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420eb",
      "text": "\t意味のない悪態をつきたいが、大抵悪態に意味のある言葉が付与されているので困る",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420ec",
      "text": "\t\t意味がないことが知られている単語：[メタ構文変数]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420ed",
      "text": "\t\tあ、そうだ。「[罵詈雑言]」って言えば良いんだ。",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420ee",
      "text": "\t\t\tba-ri-zou-gon: ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420ef",
      "text": " \t\t\tb 有声両唇破裂音、\t\ta 広母音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420f0",
      "text": " \t\t\tr 歯舌弾き音、\t\t\ti 前舌広母音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420f1",
      "text": " \t\t\tz 有声歯舌摩擦音、\t\to 後舌中母音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420f2",
      "text": " \t\t\tg 有声軟口蓋破裂音、\to 後舌中母音",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420f3",
      "text": " \t「カッパドキア」とかもリズム的に良いんだけど流石に意味が離れすぎ",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420f4",
      "text": " \t日本語以外の言語の悪態言ってみたら日本語の悪態ついたときとにた気持ちになるんだろうか[caki.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420f5",
      "text": "  \tどれどれ[Summer498.icon]",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420f6",
      "text": "   \thttps://www.gitsl.com/ala/11265/",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420f7",
      "text": "   \tMerde（糞）、Putain（売女）",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420f8",
      "text": "   \t外国語の悪態ってヒドさの方向性が違っていて、え~それは流石に、みたいになる",
      "userId": "6436266c7ac3c0001bed60e6",
      "created": 1778640597,
      "updated": 1778640597
    },
    {
      "id": "6a03e6d300000000009420f9",
